metadata.name: Sepia Memories
metadata.description:
"Sepia Memories"

My memories of this place were washed in the colors of sepia. There was a peacefulness to it, a feeling of nostalgia and contentment. It was a place that brought me back to a simpler time, a time before the worries of the world weighed heavy on my shoulders. I closed my eyes and allowed myself to drift away in the sepia-colored memories.

"Often times, our memories of travels are washed in colors of Sepia."

**"Sepia Memories" is an exclusive BWOW inspired airdrop, created by DeltaSauce, for holders of "By Way of Water"**
